<F P=104>  Tallinn BNS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Riga, Jan 20, BNS -- The Latvian Government is 
working to strengthen the country's bounday with eastern 
neighbors, Defense Minister Valdis Pavlovskis told the Saeima 
plenary session Thursday [20 January]. 
  Pavlovskis was asked by MP [member of parliament] Juris 
