<H3> <TI>   Grachev To Reorganize Defense Ministry </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2101205494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1930 GMT 
21 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2101205494 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [From the "Radio Slavyanka" program of the Russian Defense </F>
Ministry] 
  [Text] Army General Pavel Grachev, Russian defense 
minister, has made the decision to reorganize certain structures 
in the Defense Ministry. The main directorate for work with 
personnel has been reorganized into the directorate for 
indoctrination and the main directorate for training and 
placement of cadres is to become the main directorate for 
personnel. The reorganization of these bodies is being 
undertaken to improve indoctrination, combat, and 
moral-psychological training and military education in the 
Russian Armed Forces. 

</TEXT>

