<F P=100> UKRAINE </F>
<F P=101> International Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Foreign Ministry Protests Romanian Reports </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2201153894 Kiev UKRINFORM in Ukrainian 1348 GMT 22 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2201153894 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UKRINFORM </F>


