<H3> <TI>   Ioseliani: Mkhedrioni `Must Liquidate Themselves' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2101152094 Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network in Georgian 1400 
GMT 21 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2101152094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi Radio Tbilisi Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] In Jaba Ioseliani's opinion, the Mkhedrioni 
[horsemen; pro-governmental militia] units must liquidate 
themselves. Jaba Ioseliani, the leader of the Mkhedrioni, the 
chairman of the interim committee for emergencies in Georgia, in 
a conversation with journalists, when asked as to which 
structures should the Mkhedrioni members be united, answered 
that it was a personal affair of each member of the 
organization, though most of them would, probably, enter the 
rescue corps. 

