<H3> <TI>   Russian Troops Strike Opposition Strongholds, Mojahedin </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2601072994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0715 GMT 26 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2601072994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Roman Zadunaiskiy] </F>
  [Text] Moscow January 26 TASS -- The Russian border guards 
in Tajikistan delivered two preventive strikes overnight on the 
strongholds of Tajik opposition and Mojahedin in Afghanistan and 
on the routes which the militants were expected to use to 
penetrate in Tajikistan, a spokesman of the Russian frontier 
troops in Moscow told TASS on Wednesday. 
  The spokesman gave no further details. 

</TEXT>

