<F P=100> Moldova </F>
<H3> <TI>   Snegur, Experts Examine Proposals on Ilascu Group </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU2601120294 Chisinau BASAPRESS in English 1908 GMT 24 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU2601120294 </F>
<F P=104>  Chisinau BASAPRESS </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Chisinau BASAPRESS, 24/1/1994 -- Today, President 
Mircea Snegur met at his request with heads of Moldovan justice 
bodies, says a communique of the presidential press service. 
Ways to solve the problem of the so-called Ilascu group 
prisoners in the context of proposals by CSCE and the Council of 
Europe groups of experts and by the European Union and Russia 
were discussed during their meeting. It was stressed that the 
support of international organizations was very important. The 
participants in the discussion expressed their readiness to 
analyze the suggestions of international experts, taking into 
the account the statements made by President Snegur. According 
to his statements, the prisoners should be transferred to 
Moldovan constitutional justice bodies, states the communique. 

</TEXT>

