<F P=100> Lithuania </F>
<H3> <TI>   Seimas Objects to Agricultural Reform Decision </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2001093294 Vilnius Radio Vilnius International Service in 
Lithuanian 2200 GMT 19 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2001093294 </F>
<F P=104>  Vilnius Radio Vilnius International Service </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Lithuanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Lithuanian Constitutional Court decided on 
Wednesday that the Seimas decision on the main guidelines of 
agricultural reform was in its form contrary to the 
Constitution. The document adopted by the Seimas on the 
initiative of the majority of the Lithuanian Democratic Labour 
Party last June has provoked dissatisfaction of some strata of 
the society and of the Seimas opposition. According to them, 
the main guidelines of agricultural reform were hampering a 
historically just restoration of land property in the country. 

</TEXT>

